== German ==

=== Etymology ===

:''[[diminutive]] form of ''[[Teekessel]]'', "teapot".''

=== Noun ===

'''Teekesselchen''' ''n.''

# A [[small]] [[teapot]]
# ''A word with multiple distinct, unrelated meanings''
#:"Das Wort "Bauer" ist ein Teekesselchen." &mdash; "The word "[[Bauer]]" is a Teekesselchen."

